  <brief_title>Canadian Study of Trandolapril on Blood Pressure in Hypertensive Patients (TRAIL)</brief_title>
  <acronym>TRAIL</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open-Label Study to Evaluate the Effect of an Escalating Dose Regimen of Trandolapril on Blood Pressure in Treatment-Na√Øve and Concurrently Treated Hypertensive Patients (TRAIL)</official_title>
