  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The TRAIL study was conducted to examine the effects of escalating doses of an ACE inhibitor,
      trandolapril, on lowering blood pressure in Stage 1-2 hypertensive patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
